Martin Hewitt (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Martin_Hewitt_(actor) 0 Martin Hewitt (born February 19, 1958 in San Jose, California) is an American actor. He is best known for his film debut as David Axelrod in Franco Zeffirelli's Endless Love (1981). Martin_Hewitt ( born February_19_,_1958 in San_Jose , California ) is an_American_actor .
